    "1400131": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Lynette",
                    "T": "...Ah. You're back."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lynette",
                    "T": "You were so quick. I've only just finished my third dessert."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lyney",
                    "T": "Your third!? Lynette, come on, we've talked about this, everything in moderation... You're not gonna have any room left for dinner now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lynette",
                    "T": "That's fine. I'll shift to Exercise Mode and jog off the excess sugar."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lyney",
                    "T": "That's besides the point... *sigh* Well, it's done now. But try to eat a more balanced diet in the future."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lynette",
                    "T": "Point taken."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jemma",
                    "T": "Did... everything go okay?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Of course. Lorenzo was no match for us! The Gardes are taking him into custody as we speak."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jemma",
                    "T": "Gosh. That's amazing... I'm sorry, I still didn't know if I could trust you, but now it seems I can."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jemma",
                    "T": "I had my suspicions about Lorenzo, but I... *sob*"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "It's okay, we understand. He did threaten you. Paimon would find it hard to trust strangers in your position too."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "But you don't need to be scared anymore. Everything's gonna be okay!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jemma",
                    "T": "Sorry... Sorry, my emotions are all over the place right now. I've been waiting for this day to come for so long."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jemma",
                    "T": "I always wanted to report Lorenzo. He took all of Cesar's property, which I found suspicious, but I had people watching me all the time, so I couldn't risk looking into it..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jemma",
                    "T": "I was so afraid... I was scared he'd do something terrible to me, and then no one would be left to visit Cesar's grave... so I never had the courage to speak out."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jemma",
                    "T": "Thank you all, truly. Thank you so much..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
